        "timestamp": "2020-02-13 17:57:45.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nIt is a new implementation option in which endpoint accepts an application/json or application/xacml+xml payload. Typically it is a string passed into the provider. The native application and its translator will translate the string into xacml request based on the content-type.\n\nI use JsonRequestTranslator.load(string) and DOMRequest.load(string) inspired by their usage in XACMLPdpServlet (github xacml). @Pam, please let me know if it is what you are looking for. If so, I'll add in the junits.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
